headline: Elevance Health (ELV) Margin Decline Challenges Bullish Earnings Growth Narratives
summary: Elevance Health (ELV) is expected to grow earnings by 10.78% per year, with annual revenue growth forecast at 5.2%. While net profit margins have narrowed to 2.8% from 3.7% last year, the company has delivered 3.8% annual earnings growth over the past five years and maintains a reputation for high-quality earnings. Investors are eyeing these results for signs of ongoing profit and revenue growth, appealing valuation, and dividend potential, particularly with steady, if unspectacular, profit...
